            <title>[HBASE-2824] Add a filter that randomly included rows based on a configured chance.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-2824</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We needed a filter that allows us to randomly include rows. I will attach a patch with a simple Filter that is able to do this.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For example, if you wish to do a scan but only want 1/4 of all values (randomly distributed), you can use: new RandomRowFilter(0.25f)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I just wanted to share this Filter with you. It&apos;s up to you if you want to include it in the codebase.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
